room_title: Escape room "Time Paradox" by Amazing Escape Room in Freehold
review: I have been there with a group of friends twice now in 2 weeks. We tried the Time Paradox room the first time and the Wizard room just yesterday. We've had a blast both times and have not yet been disappointed. We are coming back next month to celebrate my boyfriend's birthday. Hoping to get the Wild West room. I'm totally looking forward to it!

room_title: Escape room "Time Paradox" by Amazing Escape Room in Freehold
review: We went here for Mother's Day and did the Time Paradox room with Mary, who was very helpful and friendly! The room wasn't too easy, so I wouldn't recommend it for kids. It was tough to get going but we figured it out with 15 minutes to spare, second best time of the day!
